<og:title>Updated B2 Cloud Storage Integrations and Customer Stories</og:title>
<og:description>Over the past few months we have added certified integrations with GoodSync, Arq, Panic, UpdraftPlus, Morro Data, QNAP, Archiware, Restic, and more.</og:description>
<og:url>https://www.backblaze.com/blog/b2-cloud-storage-roundup/</og:url>
<og:image>https://www.backblaze.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/b2-integrator-roundup.jpg</og:image>
