<og:title>2017 Hard Drive Reliability by Drive Size and Brand</og:title>
<og:description>We take a look at the performance of our 86,529 hard drives and break down the failure rates by manufacturer and model size.</og:description>
<og:url>https://www.backblaze.com/blog/hard-drive-failure-rates-q3-2017/</og:url>
<og:image>https://www.backblaze.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/blog-header-drive-stats-q3-2017.jpg</og:image>
