<og:title>How to Backup Linux With Duplicity and Restic</og:title>
<og:description>Linux users have a variety of options for handling data backup. We take a look at two of the most popular, Duplicity and Restic.</og:description>
<og:url>https://www.backblaze.com/blog/backing-linux-backblaze-b2-duplicity-restic/</og:url>
<og:image>https://www.backblaze.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/linux_duplicity_restic_header2.png</og:image>
<dc:language>en-US</dc:language>
<dc:format>text/html</dc:format>
